name: Incoherent Thoughts Concerning Love - Giclée Print
description:
Giclée (canvas) print of my original painting from my "Incoherent Thoughts" series.  Hand signed by artist. 

Open edition. Image is 24"x24" with white border. Total dimensions are 26"x26".  

Prints can be canvas wrapped or framed,  please contact me for pricing on these options.

Prints are shipped via UPS. Allow 7-10 days after purchase date for delivery. 
*colours are slightly off in photo and vary based on monitor
